        {
            "title": "亞洲外匯在伊朗戰爭訊號混雜中掙扎尋找方向",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/77zs9PzzqkXlETvRd7xjkA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC37002_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週一亞洲貨幣掙扎尋找方向,美元則保持堅挺,投資者在中東地區地緣政治風險升高與有關恢復停火外交的報導之間尋求平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數上漲0.1%,延續近期漲勢。截至美國東部時間02:52(格林威治標準時間06:52),美元指數期貨也上漲0.1%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>川普為伊朗設定最後期限;Axios報導停火談判</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易員關注美國總統川普為伊朗設定的最後期限,要求其在週二晚間前重新開放荷莫茲海峽。川普表示,德黑蘭必須在美國東部時間晚上8:00前恢復油輪通過這條戰略水道的交通,否則將面臨對關鍵基礎設施的攻擊,包括發電廠和橋樑。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b872eb4c-2d08-3b66-9fb7-4742e2968f21-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在Axios報導稱美國、伊朗和區域調解者正在討論可能達成45天停火協議的條款後,市場情緒略有改善,儘管尚未確認取得突破。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元匯率持平,而韓元兌美元匯率下跌0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">區域貨幣也受到油價影響,油價在前一交易日飆升後仍維持高位。原油價格上漲往往會對亞洲貨幣造成壓力,因為這會惡化日本、韓國和印度等主要進口國的貿易平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣在岸兌美元匯率下跌0.1%,而新加坡元兌美元匯率持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳元兌美元匯率上漲0.3%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度盧比下跌;印度央行本週將作出決定</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週一印度盧比兌美元匯率跳升0.6%至93.281盧比,此前在上一交易日觸及逾兩週低點92.585盧比。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該貨幣在過去五個交易日上漲,得益於該國央行的支持措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場正等待印度儲備銀行將於週三公布的利率決定,儘管盧比下滑,但預期將維持利率不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者也在評估週五公布的好於預期的美國就業數據,這強化了市場對聯準會可能在更長時間內維持高利率的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F%E6%B7%B7%E9%9B%9C%E4%B8%AD%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91-075725146.html",
