            "title": "伊朗最高領袖、領袖顧問強硬回應川普！伊朗公佈擊落12架美國戰機清單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkKzUcrLgRKq.LdvTqomdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/d89ec956a5cc38da20689cb67a59a963\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96-%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%BC%B7%E7%A1%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E8%90%BD12%E6%9E%B6%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE-070003851.html",
